-- Six Killed in Gun Attack in India’s Assam State, PTI Reports
-- B y   K a r t i k   G o y a l
-- 2013-11-04T03:11:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-04/six-killed-in-gun-attack-in-india-s-assam-state-pti-reports.html
At least six people were killed and
seven injured in a suspected terrorist attack in  India ’s
northeastern state of Assam, the Press Trust of India reported,
citing people it didn’t identify.  Unidentified gunmen opened fire on a group of people in
Assam’s Goalpara district last night, the news agency reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
